title: 820-2915 not turning on
message:
Have a 820-2915 with soda damage. Replaced everything affected by the spill but still no fan spin.

Checked power rails and pp5v_sus is pulsing up to 0.135V then 0v. Replaced Q7840 and D2400 but same results. Checked and have no shorts. Drawing steady 0.15amps on power supply

What to try next?

title: 820-2915 not turning on
message: Just warning even if if you fix this it will have a dead GPU

title: 820-2915 not turning on
